data.value: In order to navigate your way thoguh the application you need to look on the left hand side of the application. Here you will find a selection of navigation buttons. If ypou click on one of these buttons it will take you to the relevent page, for example if you were to click the My Books button you will be navigated to the 'My Books' page where you can view all the books that you have out on loan. If you were to click on the search book button the application would then navigate you the page where you can search for a book and then rent that particular book
